Nemesis Enforcer/Scattershot:



Scattershot looked to Nemesis Enforcer, a camera viewed on 
Wheeljack.  "Shall I let him in?"

"Sure."

"Alright." Scattershot activated the intercom for the outside of the 
ship.  "This is Scattershot, you may enter, at your own risk." the 
entry hatch opened for Wheeljack to enter through.
